==Irish==
===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|[ˈagəv&#690;]}}
===Prepositional pronoun===
[[Second person]] [[plural]] [[pronoun]] fused with preposition [[ag]] '[[at]]'
#[[at]] [[you]] (pl.)

===Usage===
Used as the predicate of the verb [[bí]] 'to [[be]]' to indicate possession:
:''Tá leabhar agaibh'' &mdash; You (pl.) have a book

